Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.93,0:00:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, this will be worth dissecting!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.60,0:00:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Mika-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.73,0:00:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,are all those people\Ndissection masters too?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.27,0:00:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, they undertake the dissection\Nof huge dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.57,0:00:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... their tools have a very\Nparticular shape too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.53,0:00:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, man... where did\Nour vacation go...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.03,0:00:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh... booze...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.74,0:00:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,This is not what we were told...\NYesterday was fun, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.54,0:00:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sleepy...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.37,0:00:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, guys, don't be lazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.04,0:00:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, if there are dissection\Nmasters and all...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.92,0:00:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do we have to do it too?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.17,0:00:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what you get for the mess\Nyou caused at the bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.72,0:00:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop complaining and do it!\NC'mon, go to the altar!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.51,0:00:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Riiiiight...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.27,0:00:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we pray too?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.06,0:01:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.02,0:01:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,-Let's go.\N-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.77,0:01:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Rest... and return...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.90,0:01:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,To the skies, to the skies...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.32,0:01:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Be one with the earth,\None with the life...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.41,0:01:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,With the life...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.37,0:01:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Return thee... return thee...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.04,0:01:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Fortunately, no one was hurt\Nin this incident...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.42,0:01:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But the city was badly damaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.88,0:01:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We wanted to be of help\Neven if it was only a little bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.30,0:01:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So we drakers ended up helping\Nwith the dissection all together.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.97,0:01:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm more than glad to help the city,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.56,0:01:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,but...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.56,0:01:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,we can't even think about the festival now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.65,0:01:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,♪〜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.19,0:03:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,〜♪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.74,0:03:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, great, over here, don't stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.74,0:03:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Don't push it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.12,0:03:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the help, we didn't\Nhave enough people.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.17,0:03:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,No problem, I was just thinking\Nwhat should I do for the crew's lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.63,0:03:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You really don't mind\Ngiving me so many ingredients?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.59,0:03:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, since the festival was cancelled\Nwe weren't going to use them anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.38,0:03:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If they're gonna go bad,\NI'd rather use them for emergency food.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.22,0:03:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The townsfolk are working hard\Non reconstructing the city, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.23,0:03:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.69,0:03:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we're making soup?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.35,0:03:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope, it's something that was made\Nso that peasants could have lunch outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.61,0:03:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Local cuisine that can be cooked\Nin a cauldron.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.98,0:03:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ohh, then that's perfect\Nfor emergency food indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.32,0:03:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Not as much as you'd think!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.95,0:04:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.03,0:04:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Melt the dragon fat in the cauldron,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.87,0:04:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,put in some caraway and onion and\Nstir-fry it until it gets a golden colour.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.75,0:04:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.71,0:04:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you! You better not put\Npotatoes in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.75,0:04:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,-Ah... there we go.\N-Of course I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.38,0:04:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsk! We don't put that thing in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.72,0:04:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.89,0:04:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,This has no bacon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.30,0:04:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.77,0:04:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's goulash, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.52,0:04:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't fry the bacon\Nwith the onion,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.27,0:04:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,it will taste bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.19,0:04:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Katja, go get some from the\Nbar's kitchen, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.77,0:04:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.32,0:04:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave this one to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.61,0:04:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.99,0:04:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,See? I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.74,0:04:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,This kind of dish is cooked\Ndifferently in every family.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.49,0:04:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone thinks theirs is the best\Nand that's why they always argue.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.54,0:04:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.96,0:04:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, what about the meat?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.21,0:04:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,From what I see, it's all dragon meat,\Nbut of many types and parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.59,0:04:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You can put whatever meat\Nyou want, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.34,0:05:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.30,0:05:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, putting a lot of different\Nkinds of meat is the Quon city style.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.43,0:05:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep, yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.55,0:05:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.97,0:05:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a city where\Nmany different dragons gather,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.27,0:05:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,so it's a taste you only can find here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.85,0:05:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And on top of this, some meat\Ncut in big sized pieces,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.61,0:05:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,sprinkle some salt, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.61,0:05:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough powdered paprika\Nto cover all the meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.40,0:05:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh, you're putting that much?\NIt's bright red!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.66,0:05:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, garlic and\Ncelery tied with a thread.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.33,0:05:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Diced tomatoes, paprika and water...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.50,0:05:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And we let it simmer for 2 whole hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.63,0:05:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Ohh, I'm looking forward to this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.73,0:05:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you learn that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.23,0:05:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I've done it once before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.49,0:06:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, those two are good at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.29,0:06:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Gibbs-san, sorry for the wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.46,0:06:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, get up here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.29,0:06:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.17,0:06:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna scoop out some brain oil.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.17,0:06:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Brain oil?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.38,0:06:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a very high-grade oil accumulated\Nin the head. We were very lucky,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.59,0:06:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,because not all dragons have this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.35,0:06:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to get inside it\Nand pump it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.26,0:06:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait... what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.31,0:06:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Inside... its head?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.14,0:06:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh... for real?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.27,0:06:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What can we do? We're the smallest\Naround here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.61,0:06:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.28,0:06:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.53,0:06:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Takita, hurry it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.45,0:06:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.45,0:06:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so sticky...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.25,0:07:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.50,0:07:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ew, it smells fishy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.63,0:07:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,This is also a draker's job...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.76,0:07:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, when the potatoes\Nand carrots are cooked...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.64,0:07:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.43,0:07:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.81,0:07:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,-Um...\N-Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.23,0:07:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in Jiro's ship, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.65,0:07:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.69,0:07:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,How is he like?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.20,0:07:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiro, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.07,0:07:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.62,0:07:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahhh, I'm so hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.04,0:07:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,-Lunch time!\N-It smells so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.96,0:07:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Working for free sure makes you\Nhungrier than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.50,0:07:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Good job out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.50,0:07:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Katja!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.09,0:07:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You cooked too?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.80,0:07:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,-Only a bit.\N-I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.93,0:07:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, while we wait for this to\Nfinish cooking...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.10,0:07:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's make another thing over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.39,0:07:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the red meat of the dragon\Nwe brought to this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.94,0:08:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, the one I dissected!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.36,0:08:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll simply just hit it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.78,0:08:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hit it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.90,0:08:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll hit it as if we were pulling it\Nand stretch it thin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.45,0:08:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I want to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.83,0:08:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,How about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.21,0:08:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.17,0:08:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, some salt and pepper,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.96,0:08:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,sprinkle some flour,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.63,0:08:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,coat it evenly with egg\Nand cover it with cheese\Nmixed with breadcrumbs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.59,0:08:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Melt some dragon fat and butter\Nin a big frypan, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.47,0:08:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.56,0:08:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Could this be...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.86,0:08:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,-Yoshi-san, this is...!\N-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.44,0:08:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been wanting to eat it\Nfor a long time, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.61,0:08:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, that's a nice colour.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.91,0:08:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hop!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.87,0:08:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,A dragon cutlet, extra large!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.58,0:09:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh boy, what's this smell?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.08,0:09:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.33,0:09:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, this can't go wrong in any way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.17,0:09:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoshi-san, you're the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.05,0:09:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, let's eat it togeth...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.93,0:09:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.84,0:09:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Mika-san! That's for everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.06,0:09:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.35,0:09:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Someone get Mika away\Nfrom the cutlet!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.89,0:09:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,He's gonna eat it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.73,0:09:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't monopolize it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.77,0:09:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, the people from your ship\Nare always like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.07,0:09:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.07,0:09:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks so fun, how nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.70,0:09:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.73,0:09:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,"Dragon cutlet and Quon-style goulash"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.58,0:09:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So good!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.54,0:09:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Faye! Your cutlet\Nis bigger than mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.17,0:09:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw come on, you're so fussy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.85,0:09:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Gibbs, do we have any more\Nwork after this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.68,0:10:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We're supposed to continue\Nuntil sunset...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.10,0:10:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.02,0:10:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.69,0:10:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoshi-san, seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.82,0:10:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,How many seconds have you eaten?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.28,0:10:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,-Okay, line up!\N-That's unfair for the others!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.57,0:10:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a little bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.70,0:10:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,-Here, for you, Jiro.\N-Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.33,0:10:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the specialty of our city.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.46,0:10:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And we add bacon to the goulash, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.50,0:10:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.63,0:10:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! So good!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.64,0:10:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,This somehow looks...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.14,0:10:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Like a festival, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.77,0:10:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.90,0:10:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Mika-san, you're eating too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.02,0:10:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Might as well just drink some alcohol!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.65,0:10:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.32,0:10:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm joking...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.28,0:10:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I think a glass won't hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.57,0:10:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.87,0:11:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop yelling!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.87,0:11:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So... about the method\Nto extract the poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.96,0:11:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Add a lot of salt and water\Nthat has been boiled once to rice bran,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.55,0:11:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and just pickle the meat in that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.97,0:11:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Rice bran?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.34,0:11:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And that will extract the poison?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.97,0:11:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The wisdom of our ancestors is\Nnot to be taken lightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.64,0:11:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Ohh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.02,0:11:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Put the meat and the rice bran\Nalternatively in a pottery jar,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.65,0:11:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,close it with a lid, and seal it with a cloth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.82,0:11:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Bury it for about three years in the earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.90,0:11:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and wait for the poison to disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.16,0:11:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.12,0:11:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.25,0:11:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I never said that you could\Neat it right away...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.42,0:11:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Wait, Mika-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.59,0:11:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing\Nto the poor old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.97,0:11:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Three years...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.05,0:12:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Mika, help us fill the jars.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.89,0:12:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, time for us to go back\Nto our own job.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.40,0:12:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Katja! Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.12,0:12:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, I think we'll\Nfinish dissecting it today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.13,0:12:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I guess we can leave\Ntomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.88,0:12:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, please do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.93,0:12:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.59,0:12:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We were able to refuel and repair\Nthe ship, but our gains are essentially none.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.02,0:12:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't even think of a vacation...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.98,0:12:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I... guess that's true, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.40,0:12:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,My massage...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.73,0:12:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.69,0:12:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's... it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.82,0:12:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I do understand how you feel, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.15,0:13:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But we shouldn't stay long here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.57,0:13:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,For the sake of the people\Nof this city as well, we should leave soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.45,0:13:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.99,0:13:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.62,0:13:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Mika-san! You're skipping work again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.33,0:13:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha? We finished dissecting it,\Nso what does it matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.09,0:13:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.22,0:13:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We're leaving in the morning, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.89,0:13:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.47,0:13:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Too bad we couldn't see the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.97,0:13:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.60,0:13:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I really wanted to eat that dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.52,0:13:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what do you think it tastes like?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.07,0:13:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.02,0:13:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know about that yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.15,0:13:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh, good grief! It's finally over!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.99,0:13:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It took three whole days...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.37,0:13:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That dragon was way too huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.82,0:13:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all we can do.\NNow it's up to the townspeople.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.33,0:13:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Good job today!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.62,0:13:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Takita, you too, you worked hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.92,0:13:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, it's time! Time to drink!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.42,0:13:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, nice voice there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.80,0:14:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to prepare for the departure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.67,0:14:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Whaaat?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.01,0:14:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,For real...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.47,0:14:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Takita, where's Jiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.97,0:14:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't he with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.51,0:14:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He said he was going back first.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.39,0:14:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, isn't it fine?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.15,0:14:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiro...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.11,0:14:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.34,0:14:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Come with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.45,0:14:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.54,0:14:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.17,0:14:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's called autogyro.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.04,0:14:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The guys from the other ship\Ngave it to us in gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.92,0:14:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, put this on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.76,0:14:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I practiced a lot until\NI was able to ride it well!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.39,0:14:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Katja, hop on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.14,0:14:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.94,0:14:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold onto me tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.52,0:14:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.33,0:15:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Up we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.96,0:15:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.89,0:15:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm flying!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.97,0:16:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You said you had never\Nleft the city, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.56,0:16:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.07,0:16:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.78,0:16:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We're outside the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.01,0:16:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,When the sun finishes rising...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.80,0:16:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll... leave the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.07,0:17:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.57,0:17:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Katja...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.28,0:17:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.49,0:17:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,come with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.46,0:17:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,to the ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.89,0:17:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.26,0:17:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,If you talk that much...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.14,0:17:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll bite your tongue...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.67,0:18:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Ohh, it's wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.13,0:18:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much for bringing it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.55,0:18:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll add this to the tapestry too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.85,0:18:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, Takita, put out your arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.31,0:18:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.10,0:18:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.06,0:18:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an amulet I made with a scrap.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.02,0:18:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, an ointment made with the mucus\Nof a small kind of dragon called salamandra.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.36,0:18:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good for erasing scars.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.16,0:18:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanami-san... Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.95,0:18:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure you come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.58,0:18:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yesh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.04,0:18:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna leave, get boarding!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.59,0:18:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Riiiight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.63,0:18:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Be well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.42,0:18:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,For the time you come back,\Nthe meat will most likely be edible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.76,0:18:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You better leave some for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.39,0:19:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Back to living in the sky again, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.02,0:19:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The sky's our lover, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.69,0:19:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,-Sadly...\N-What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.86,0:19:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I should get going too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.36,0:19:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, Katja...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.87,0:19:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.08,0:19:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Katja...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.38,0:19:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna cut your hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.13,0:19:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.55,0:19:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,With this, you kind of\Nlook like a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.09,0:19:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't take me more than five minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.09,0:19:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you lend me scissors and a sheet?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.55,0:19:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,S-sure, I think we have some in the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.60,0:19:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Vannie!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.68,0:19:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you lend me a pair of scissors?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.48,0:19:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll return them right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.52,0:19:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure... take your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.70,0:19:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad I met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.78,0:20:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.72,0:20:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Three years, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.02,0:20:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on... are you still going on\Nabout that, Mika-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.95,0:20:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Freshen up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.70,0:20:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Mika!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.95,0:20:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go to the lookout.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.79,0:20:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.79,0:20:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,-Hm?\N-Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.04,0:20:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiro-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.21,0:20:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?! What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.04,0:20:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does it matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.00,0:20:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be at the front and\Nyou at the back, Mika.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.55,0:21:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,U-um, Jiro-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.51,0:21:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Takita.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.55,0:21:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Boys have a lot going on for them, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.10,0:21:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be at the front.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.60,0:21:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,No, me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.02,0:21:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, it'll be me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.10,0:21:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No way in hell, me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.73,0:21:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,-Me at the front!\N-Me!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.11,0:21:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,-Me.\N-Me, me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.36,0:21:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,No, me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.32,0:21:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,-No, I'll be the one!\N-Me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.78,0:21:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?! I'm also an adult now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.95,0:21:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, be my guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.20,0:21:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,♪〜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.07,0:22:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Translation: akemilena   Proofreading: TomoyaNC
